(15, 'samsung_powerbot_vr7000_robot_vacuum', 'Samsung Powerbot VR7000 Robot Vacuum', 'Clean your floors with minimal effort with the Samsung POWERbot VR7000 Robot Vacuum. Coming in at 28% thinner than previous models, this device packs a lot of power. The VR7000 Robot Vacuum is able to generate up to 20 watts of suction power.', '', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Clean your floors with minimal effort with the&nbsp;</span><a href="http://thegadgetflow.com/portfolio/h7-wireless-speaker/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 141, 187); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);" target="_blank">Samsung</a><span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">&nbsp;POWERbot VR7000 Robot Vacuum. Coming in at 28% thinner than previous models, this device packs a lot of power. The VR7000 Robot Vacuum is able to generate up to 20 watts of suction power. It also uses an Edge Clean Master feature that can pick up debris as close as .5&rdquo; from a wall. In addition to these features, the POWERbot VR7000 is intelligent for a smarter clean. It has Visionary Mapping Plus and FullView Sensor 2.0. This vacuum can actually remember the layout of the room to ensure a thorough clean. Finally, the Intelligent Power Control feature helps it complete high-quality cleanings. The VR7000 will automatically adjust to different floor types with no human intervention.</span></p>\r\n', '', '0', 'aac0e-samsung-powerbot-vr7000-robot-vacuum-02.jpg', '0c8ce-samsung-powerbot-vr7000-robot-vacuum-04.jpg', '', '', '4', 425, 4, '1', '', '', '', '2017-03-04 05:07:02'),
