(17, 'nanit_baby_monitor_and_sleep_tracker', 'Nanit Baby Monitor and Sleep Tracker', 'Introducing Nanit, the Baby Monitor and Sleep Tracker for parents of the 21st century. This revolutionary system consists of a night vision camera as well as a motion sensor', '', '<p>\r\n	<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qASwMefxodM" width="560"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Introducing Nanit, the Baby Monitor and&nbsp;</span><a href="http://thegadgetflow.com/portfolio/moon-beam-activity-sleep-tracker-amazfit/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 141, 187); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Sleep Tracker</a><span style="color: rgb(99, 105, 127); font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">&nbsp;for parents of the 21st century. This revolutionary system consists of a night vision camera as well as a motion sensor that remains above your baby&rsquo;s crib or bed. To help your baby drift off to sleep, the Nanit Baby Monitor has nature soundtracks and can also produce white noise for a relaxing environment. With built-in temperature and humidity sensors, you can be alerted if the conditions in your nursery are keeping your baby from a restful night&rsquo;s sleep. Syncing with an app on your smartphone, if the Nanit Baby Monitor detects noise or movement, you&rsquo;ll instantly receive a notification rather than have to lug around and listen to a garbled baby monitor.</span></p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	5ad26-nanit-baby-monitor-and-sleep-tracker-02.jpg</p>\r\n', '0', '64c99-141.jpg', '35859-143.jpg', '0d7b9-142.jpg', '', '4', 567, 4, '1', '', '', '', '2017