(8, 'cruzr_-_a_cloud-based_intelligent_humanoid_service_robot', 'Cruzr - a Cloud-Based Intelligent Humanoid Service Robot', '<p>\r\n	Cruzr is the First Customized Service Robot Adaptable to a Variety of Business Needs, Optimizing Human Resources and Improving Work Efficiency</p>\r\n', 'Humanoid Design with Flexible Arm | Voice Recognition & Interaction | Remote Centralized Control System | SLAM (Simultaneous Localization & Mapping) | Intelligent Customer Service | Video Conferencing | Facial Recognitio | Video Surveillance | Automatic Self-Recharging', '<p background-color:="" font-size:="" helvetica="" lucida="" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ">\r\n	&quot;Cruzr&rsquo;s mission is to improve your business, collaboration and overall quality of life,&rdquo; said John Rhee, General Manager, North America, UBTECH. &ldquo;With Cruzr, companies can better attend to their customers&rsquo; needs, while allowing human teams to focus on more complex issues requiring human interaction. Ultimately, Cruzr enables companies to spend more time making smarter business decisions.&quot;</p>\r\n<p background-color:="" font-size:="" helvetica="" lucida="" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ">\r\n	<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="473" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/20Qh9hYavIo?feature=oembed" style="border-width: initial; border-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; width: 840px;" width="840"></iframe></p>\r\n<p background-color:="" font-size:="" helvetica="" lucida="" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ">\r\n	Cruzr is truly where service meets intelligence, creating value for your business. Key features of Cruzr include:</p>\r\n<ul background-color:="" font-size:="" helvetica="" lucida="" style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 24px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ">\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>Humanoid Design with Flexible Arms</b>&nbsp;&ndash; Cruzr moves like a human and can greet visitors, shake hands, move around, dance, and even hug.</li>\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>Voice Recognition &amp; Interaction</b>&nbsp;&ndash; Cruzr recognizes people by voice, turns to face them when they speak, and can immediately reply. Cruz can also engage in casual conversation.</li>\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>Remote Centralized Control System</b>&nbsp;&ndash; With its cloud-based robotic operating system, Cruzr can set up multi-angle advertisements, real-time video surveillance, and move multiple devices at once.</li>\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>SLAM (Simultaneous Localization &amp; Mapping)</b>&nbsp;&ndash; Cruzr works like a mobile map, with smart localization and a mapping function that can guide you anywhere.</li>\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>Intelligent Customer Service</b>&nbsp;&ndash; With a customized Q&amp;A library, Cruzr can answer basic customer queries or instantaneously transfer special questions to offsite specialists for improved customer service efficiency.</li>\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>Video Conferencing</b>&nbsp;&ndash; With built-in 13MP HD Camera, Cruzr provides video conferencing, coupling high quality video and audio with the freedom of motion to move about in the meeting space.</li>\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>Facial Recognition</b>&nbsp;&ndash; Cruzr can recognize customers accurately and respond accordingly.</li>\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>Video Surveillance &ndash;&nbsp;</b>Cruzr&rsquo;s video surveillance system and autonomous security-patrolling skills send out alert notices via APP, recording video to keep your business protected 24/7.</li>\r\n	<li class="bwlistitemmargb" style="margin-bottom: 2px;">\r\n		<b>Automatic Self-Recharging</b>&nbsp;&ndash; Cruzr&rsquo;s battery provides 5-8 hours of active use. When its battery is low, Cruzr will automatically return to its self-recharging dock.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p background-color:="" font-size:="" helvetica="" lucida="" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ">\r\n	Cruzr will be available for purchase in June 2017 and is the latest UBTECH offering to coincide with the company&rsquo;s mission to bring robots into every home, and truly integrate intelligent robots into the daily life of everyone, creating a more intelligent and human-friendly way of leisure life.</p>\r\n', '<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;"><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr</strong>&nbsp;is a&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">hum</span><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">anoid robot</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;created by&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">UBTec</span><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">h Robotics</span></strong>&nbsp;one of&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">robotics </span><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">companies</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;based in China&#39;s Shenzhen.&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr</strong>&nbsp;is a&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">service robot</strong>&nbsp;, designed to work in medical offices, banks, shopping centers, and other similar contexts, it can perform a range of activities at our place.</span></span></p>\r\n<div open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;">After&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Alpha 2</span></strong>&nbsp;,&nbsp;<b style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">humanoid</span></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;designed to entertain and make life easier for families, and&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">robots</span></strong>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">educational robotics</span></strong>&nbsp;, UBTech launches a new&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">android</span></strong>&nbsp;, a&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">service robot</strong>&nbsp;, designed to work.</span></span></div>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;">So do not talk in this case of a&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">household robot</span></strong>&nbsp;but of a different field of&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">robotics</span></strong>&nbsp;, designed to help companies improve the services provided to customers and perform a number of internal activities of the company.&nbsp;Now let us see how.</span></span></p>\r\n<h2 font-size:="" line-height:="" open="" style="border: none; margin: 30px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;"><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr robot, what it can do</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;"><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr robots</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;can work in several sectors and business and commercial contexts.&nbsp;UBTech has presented at CES 2017, the consumer electronics show held every year in Las Vegas, calling it the first&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">service robots</strong>&nbsp;fully customizable based on the needs of companies.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;">The&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">service robot</strong>&nbsp;together with&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">c</span><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">obot</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;carry the &#39;&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">artificial in</span><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">telligence</span></strong>&nbsp;inside companies and are an evolution of industrial robots that have begun to work in factories since the early seventies.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;"><img alt="cruzr-robot" class="size-full wp-image-17263 alignright" data-id="17263" height="202" src="https://www.robotiko.it/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/cruzr-robot.jpg" style="border: none; margin: 5px 0px 20px 20px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; float: right;" width="319" />The&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr robots</strong>&nbsp;can perform customer service functions, ie all activities related to the relationship with customers before and after the purchase of a good or a service.&nbsp;This means that&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr robots</strong>&nbsp;can provide customer service before the purchase of an asset, informing them about the characteristics of an object or of a commercial item, and can answer questions and requests for assistance even after the customer has purchased that particular article.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;"><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr robot</strong>&nbsp;moves on wheels is able to recognize faces and to perceive the emotional state of its human interlocutor.&nbsp;It features localization and mapping systems that allow it to orient within the environment and is capable of video surveillance of large areas (eg a shopping center) 24 hours 24.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;">Robots as&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr</strong>&nbsp;could be used in the future in airports and train stations, to give information to travelers and tourists, but also as part of security systems.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr and other service robots</strong></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;">The&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">service robotics</strong>&nbsp;, as well as that of&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">home rob</span><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">ots</span></strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">perso</span><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">nal robots</span></strong>&nbsp;, it is intended to know an exponential growth in the coming years.&nbsp;The robotics companies are working to get&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">rob</span><span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;">ots</span></strong>&nbsp;more and more reliable and efficient.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><img alt="robot-humanoid-models-romeo" class="wp-image-6661 alignleft" data-id="6661" height="159" src="https://www.robotiko.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/robot-umanoidi-modelli-romeo.jpg" style="border: none; margin: 5px 20px 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; float: left;" width="160" />Romeo robot</strong>&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;">is a</span><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;robot for the elderly</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;which was designed by Softbank Robotics (the French company before the acquisition by Softbank called</span><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;Aldebaran Robotics</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;).&nbsp;In the coming years we may see it at work in nursing homes for the elderly.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><a href="https://www.robotiko.it/r1-robot/" style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(118, 169, 52);"><span style="color:#000000;">R1 robot</span></a><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;is a domestic android created by &#39;</span><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;Institute&nbsp;<img alt="robot-r1-robots-caregiver" class="wp-image-14354 alignleft" data-id="14354" height="102" src="https://www.robotiko.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/robot-r1-robot-badante.jpg" style="border: none; margin: 5px 20px 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; float: left;" width="164" />of National Technology</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;in Genoa but can be used as service robots in nursing homes.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img alt="pepper-robot-crociera_2" class="wp-image-11800 alignleft" data-id="11800" height="92" src="https://www.robotiko.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/pepper-robot-crociera_2.jpg" style="border: none; margin: 5px 20px 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; float: left;" width="132" />Robot Pepper</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;has a soul from</span><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;social robots</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;, is a robot for families, but in the business version can also be used by companies.&nbsp;For example, he has already been working on board cruise ships, in some shops and in banks (you can read about:</span><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;Pepper Robot goes Cruise, here&#39;s where you can find it</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;.</span></span></p>\r\n<p open="" style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: medium; font-family: ">\r\n	<span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color:#000000;">Among the&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">service robots</strong>&nbsp;is also the&nbsp;</span><strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">robot butler</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp;&nbsp;for hotels.&nbsp;In short, the future of service robots as&nbsp;<strong style="border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Cruzr</strong>&nbsp;seems just begun.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1', '84700-71.jpg', 'dffd8-72.jpg', '', '', '10', 0, 0, 'Robot, Cruzr, Intelligent, Cloud', 'rb21ub13', '', '2017-03-18 09:55:09'),
(9, 'alpha_1s_the_fun_family_robot', 'Alpha 1S - The Fun Family Robot', '<p>\r\n	Alpha 1S will be your favorite entertainment companion. Entertain or compete with your peers. Have the freedom to learn, program, and share your demonstrations, dances, yoga moves, and martial arts. Also Bluetooth all your hot music hits via your iPhone, Android, or PC. The Alpha 1S has the capability to move up to 180 degrees of rotation for maximum agility.</p>\r\n', 'Learn from your robot; it will demonstrate yoga moves, exercise moves, kung fu moves, dancing, and much more! Download and share your content with other users | Alpha 1S App to control your robot (iOS and Android) via Bluetooth 4.0 | 16 Patent Servo, Alpha 1S is highly flexible and can move just like a human | Free software to program your robot on UBTECH website. 3D visual PC software for complete beginners and advanced programmers. User friendly GUI Interface to maximize your personal experience | Free creative content to upload to your robot on UBTECH website', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="feature" data-feature-name="aplus" id="aplus_feature_div" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">\r\n	<div class="a-section a-spacing-extra-large bucket" id="aplus" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;">\r\n		<div cel_widget_id="aplus" class="aplus-v2 desktop celwidget" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: table; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;">\r\n			<div cel_widget_id="aplus-module-3" class="celwidget aplus-module module-3" style="box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 979px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px;">\r\n				<div aria-live="polite" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="700" data-a-expander-name="aplus-module-expander" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 979px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; max-height: 700px;">\r\n					<div aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden; position: relative;">\r\n						<div class="aplus-module-wrapper apm-floatnone" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; display: inline-block; float: none;">\r\n							<div class="apm-sidemodule apm-spacing" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; zoom: 1; margin: 0px auto; width: 970px; padding: 0px; position: relative;">\r\n								<div class="apm-sidemodule-textleft" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 630px; position: relative; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; padding-left: 200px; height: 300px; max-height: 300px;">\r\n									<h3 class="a-spacing-mini" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.255; margin-bottom: 6px !important;">\r\n										9 Major Humanoid Features about your Robot</h3>\r\n									<p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 14px;">\r\n										Advanced Engineered Patented Servo Joints.</p>\r\n									<p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 14px;">\r\n										Aluminum alloy with Pure White Servo Armour.</p>\r\n									<p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 14px;">\r\n										Anti-Pinch Structure Design.</p>\r\n									<p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 14px;">\r\n										Quick Charge and Long Play Time.</p>\r\n									<p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 14px;">\r\n										True Enhanced Structure.</p>\r\n									<p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding