to 84&quot;</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<h2 class="right-side" style="margin: 0px; padding-top: 25px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 10px; outline: none; word-break: normal; font-size: 32px; font-weight: normal; font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; padding-left: 580px !important;">\r\n		USB Powered</h2>\r\n	<ul class="right-side" style="padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 5px; outline: none; word-break: normal; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); margin: 0px !important; padding-left: 580px !important;">\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; list-style: circle inside url(&quot;//cdn6.bigcommerce.com/r-678b8dcecd8097c9a0dc483a251b63f87782244e/themes/ClassicNext/images/product_libg.jpg&quot;);">\r\n			Energy Efficient without sacrificing performance</li>\r\n		<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; list-style: circle inside url(&quot;//cdn6.bigcommerce.com/r-678b8dcecd8097c9a0dc483a251b63f87782244e/themes/ClassicNext/images/product_libg.jpg&quot;);">\r\n			Size range from 32&quot; to 84&quot;</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="g5-smooth" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; width: 960px; height: 551px; background-image: url(&quot;http://cdn6.bigcommerce.com/s-b60ph/product_images/uploaded_images/g5-smooth.jpg&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">\r\n	<h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 10px; outline: none; word-break: normal; font-size: 32px; font-weight: normal; font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n		250 FPS, Lightning Speed</h2>\r\n	<p class="subtitle" style="outline: none; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 20px; float: none; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 0px 5px !important; padding: 0px 30px 0px 0px !important; border: 0px solid !important; background: url(&quot;//cdn6.bigcommerce.com/r-678b8dcecd8097c9a0dc483a251b63f87782244e/themes/ClassicNext/images/icon_arrow_down.png&quot;) right center no-repeat !important;">\r\n		Higher FPS, Smoother Curve</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; outline: none; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(119, 119, 119);">\r\n		Touch screens with a higher refresh rate provides a faster response to your movements. Furthermore, it detects even the slightest actions, offering more accurate data positioning with very little latency giving the G5 Touch Screens the capability to draw very smooth &amp; accurate curves.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="g5-footer-bg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 50px 0px 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; width: 1000px; height: 1755px; background-image: url(&quot;http://cdn6.bigcommerce.com/s-b60ph/product_images/uploaded_images/g5-footer-bg.png&quot;); background-repeat: repeat-x; background-color: rgb(211, 211, 211); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">\r\n	<div id="g5-footer-value" style="margin: -20px auto 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; width: 1000px; height: auto;">\r\n		<h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 10px; outline: none; word-break: normal; font-size: 32px; font-weight: normal; font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;">\r\n			Not Just Touch</h2>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://cdn6.bigcommerce.com/s-b60ph/product_images/uploaded_images/g5-footer-value.png" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" /></div>\r\n	<div id="g5-footer-highlights" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; width: 1000px; height: auto;">\r\n		<h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 10px; outline: none; word-break: normal; font-size: 32px; font-weight: normal; font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;">\r\n			G5: The Best Large-Format Touch Screen You Can Buy</h2>\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://cdn6.bigcommerce.com/s-b60ph/product_images/uploaded_images/g5-footer-highlights.png" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; word-break: normal; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '1', '4cd4c-101.jpg', '463d4-105.jpg', 'd6484-104.jpg', '71354-102.jpg', '6', 0, 0, '', '', '', '2017-02-25 07:33:18');
